                                                         BUSINESS QUESTION
What behavior changes should we focus on to reduce churn? 

                                    QUERY
SELECT
CASE
WHEN days_since_last_purchase > 20 THEN 'AT RISK'
ELSE 'still customers'
END AS customers,
COUNT(*)		
customer_count
FROM ecommerce_data
GROUP BY customers;

                      Insight:
Customers who stay longer without purchasing are more likely to churn, making inactivity a key signal to monitor.

            Recommendation: 
We should track inactive customers and re-engage them early through reminders, offers, and targeted communication before they stop purchasing completely
